[No specific etiologies were reported and it is likely multiple organisms are involved.

Acre (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Acre_(state)) is a state located in the west of the North Region of Brazil and the Amazonia Legal. Located in the westernmost part of the country, at a two-hour time difference from Bras√≠lia, Acre is bordered clockwise by the Brazilian states of Amazonas and Rondonia to the north and north east, the Bolivian department of Pando to the south east, and the Peruvian regions of Madre de Dios, Ucayali and Loreto to the south and west. Its capital and largest city is Rio Branco. - Mod.LL]
